# 📊 Student Performance Analytics System

## Description

This project was developed as my **CBSE Class 12 Informatics Practices Final Practical Project**. It is a Python-based Student Performance Analytics System that analyzes and visualizes students' academic performance using data analysis and visualization techniques.

## Features

- 📈 Individual Student Performance Analysis
- 📊 Year-wise Performance Comparison
- 📚 Subject-wise Analysis
- 📉 Session-wise Comparison
- 🗄️ MySQL Database Integration
- 📊 Graphical Visualization using Matplotlib

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- MySQL

## Project Structure

```
Project.py
CodeX.py
CodeP.py
```

## Future Improvements

- GUI Interface
